## Banned Phrases — Reject on Sight

Fail the section if any banned phrase appears without immediate replacement:

| Phrase | Why rejected |
|--------|--------------|
| etc. | Hides incomplete enumeration |
| and so on | Non-specific |
| standard implementation | No technical content |
| handled elsewhere | Must cite where or UNKNOWN |
| similar logic applies | Must diff or cite |
| refer to the code | Doc must stand alone with citations |
| implementation details omitted | Opposite of docmax purpose |
| additional cases may exist | Must list or UNKNOWN register |

Also reject: "as needed", "various", "typically", "should be straightforward" when used to skip detail.

